{"tid":1054608,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"費城將禁止商舖拒收現金　保障無銀行戶口及信用卡人士","createTime":"2019-03-10T02:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T02:55:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9e2d55376399f4d533053f539f70485a756ed7","tid":1054608,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1446895_1_L_20190309203059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1446895_1_L_20190309203059.jpg&h=d432737a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國費城將會禁止店舖拒絕收取現金。<br />\n<br />\n費城市長肯尼簽署法律，表明如果店舖或食肆拒絕收取現金，將會觸犯歧視罪行，屬違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n費城認為，由於電子支付在日常生活日漸普遍，相關法律是要保障無銀行戶口及信用卡人士，有關法例將於當地7月1 日生效。<br />\n<br />\n外界形容，費城成為美國第一個城市立例拒絕無現金社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1446895-20190309.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1446895-20190309.htm&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2BIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=f733b4e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1446895-20190309.htm&h=4c28448c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1446895-20190309.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8bc489437621ab4ad0a99afaff714b97a21f9274","tid":1054608,"uid":169662,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"多此一舉"},{"pid":"807cc83c8894801768e40bdfded05c71a82bc972","tid":1054608,"uid":44211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n下下無現金又要先設有信用卡/認證<br />\n比得錢嚟都蚊訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要教識屋企長者點用"}]}